{"tid":2518392,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"對前途好迷茫，好唔好去讀航海？定係求其搵份工？還是走人？","createTime":"2021-05-06T04:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T05:41:27.000Z","uid":263448,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"382944bf4d984bf68f1b89889f07fa8784634604","tid":2518392,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:04:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由細到大都無乜長輩教我做人，指條路咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成輩人鳩流流咗廿年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出黎做野咗6~7年無乜野學到，又識唔到人，係拎到個電A牌，但又無乜用咁。<br />\n養咗個毒撚性格，無才=自卑、識人少=講野都唔圓滑、太安穩=不思進取。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢年諗，咁落去唔掂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n錢就儲咗啲，可以比首期多啲咁；投資就唔識，有心無膽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前幾個月諗，不如迫鳩自己一個去英國啦...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但依家又諗，去到我咁既性格都係學唔到幾多野，個心態又唔係掂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是上網問人，有人話：去讀航海啦！啱晒你呢啲邊緣人！又無女、啲家人又唔鐘意你，又想獨立搵多啲錢、又唔想係香港！家吓啲海員好正，間房大過香港啲劏房！係要大半年都係船到，貨船又無咁好網上，而且一放假就無收入啫！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽落好似真係啱自己呢種人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗，去到船上面穩定咗既話，都可以繼續打機、打丁、寫吓野。<br />\n周遊列國見識又多咗，又唔洗比家人日日嘈嘈住晒，至少自信心大咗，到時自己應該敢開個IG自拍扮旅人文青。<br />\n自己就廢人，就無諗過自己做船長/大俥，二三呢啲位置應該OK卦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計埋自己懶人性格，除番12個月，順利既話每個月2萬~2萬5咁。<br />\n<br />\n係怕讀完2年，1年實習，之後移民方面有阻滯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1841e167bccbf9be64789af8c119139eb27422b","tid":2518392,"uid":165665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:10:01.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"145a75872efa26cc88eac80c283c91d3cd2da6ce","tid":2518392,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:13:39.000Z","msg":"其實你有電A牌去到英國已經唔憂搵唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人工同你做航海差唔多"},{"pid":"1c22f4ee853d6b30d725d6c0e014ce54b22ec060","tid":2518392,"uid":36452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:14:49.000Z","msg":"好似自己出文咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db8bcaeee3fcf157f448ae7ae6e23aca225f982","tid":2518392,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"145a75872efa26cc88eac80c283c91d3cd2da6ce","tid":2518392,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:13:39.000Z","msg":"其實你有電A牌去到英國已經唔憂搵唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人工同你做航海差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"英國唔認我張A牌同經驗架...<br />\n有搵過，又係要讀多幾年書。<br />\n想做番果行最好考埋車牌/跟企業做。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d991f818b2612b6457d73bf252f2399baee684ad","tid":2518392,"uid":263448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c22f4ee853d6b30d725d6c0e014ce54b22ec060","tid":2518392,"uid":36452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:14:49.000Z","msg":"好似自己出文咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"無女朋友、屋企人成日丙你、搵唔多、讀書唔掂、朋友又少、無膽、自卑...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2914d4cc4e1b9fcbf48d388ddd53bb281297cee1","tid":2518392,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"how old you?<br />\n廿十歲左右行船行當十年升左做船長上番岸大把野撈, 當行十年船儲番來既錢可能到時夠你買樓<br />\n<br />\n或者有冇過來人可以分享下經驗比棲主"},{"pid":"f477e6a2f74fbf2c4e2d1ab0a9e1d92574c1f21b","tid":2518392,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5db8bcaeee3fcf157f448ae7ae6e23aca225f982","tid":2518392,"uid":263448,"